    "During training, we masked a certain percentage of tokens in the input text and trained the model to predict those masked tokens based on the context.",
    "This process helps the model to learn, understand, and generate text in a meaningful manner.",
    "A batch size of 32 was employed here, and the model was trained for 10 epochs using the Adam optimizer [42] with a learning rate of 1e-5.",
    "We also utilized gradient clipping to prevent exploding gradients during training.",
    "The BART model was implemented using the Pytorch deep learning framework."
